; Regression test for issue #1048: --pivot doesn't work with built-in properties
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1048
;
; --pivot constructed its expression using tag("X") which only finds metadata
; tags, not built-in properties like commodity or payee.  The fix uses
; has_tag("X") ? tag("X") : X so that metadata tags take priority, with
; built-in properties as fallback.

2014-05-31 * Test
    A         10.00 GBP
    B

2014-05-31 * Test
    A         10.00 EUR
    B

2014-05-31 * Test
    A          5.00 GBP
    B

test bal A --pivot commodity --no-total
           10.00 EUR
           15.00 GBP  commodity
           10.00 EUR    EUR:A
           15.00 GBP    GBP:A
end test

test bal A --account commodity --no-total
           10.00 EUR  EUR:A
           15.00 GBP  GBP:A
end test
